## 1. Task Intent Interpretation

### 1.1 Problem Summary

The NuttyFans project requires a foundational Next.js scaffold that:
- Enforces architectural rules from day one
- Prevents ad-hoc patterns and tooling inconsistency
- Enables safe AI-assisted development
- Scales like a large engineering organization

### 1.2 Business Context

Per `docs/01-BRD.md`:
- NuttyFans is a creator monetization platform
- Target: $10M GMV in Year 1
- Stack decision: Next.js (App Router), TypeScript, PostgreSQL, Tailwind + ShadCN
- Architecture: Modular monolith with future microservice extraction path

### 1.3 Scope Boundaries

| In Scope | Out of Scope |
